title: The Track 1 Rankings
description:
The last time we did this, there were hurt feelings and some loss of respect. Can we handle the rankings this time? Prob not but we do it again! Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey rank all of the track ones in Taylor's discography!
Where do your rankings fall? And what would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
